{"tid":1502342,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"非分化 但推機場既巴絲講野前可唔可以用下腦","createTime":"2019-08-24T15:49:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-24T17:23:09.000Z","uid":43994,"like":17,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"bf6b7f48afd4b2b20d5d6c80809679e38171b271","tid":1502342,"uid":43994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T15:49:22.000Z","msg":"今日成日睇Live post又好其他post又好，見到好多巴絲叫人去機場<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">我先唔講上晝去機場下晝去遊行抗爭呢樣野，對手足體力既負擔有幾大<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n亦唔講遊行搞手花左幾多時間做宣傳，準備物資申請不反對通知書，拉一堆人去機場只會分散晒手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>我只係講一樣野，就係某啲叫人去機場既巴絲講野好難聽</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一係就用情緒勒索，叫人入機場<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hFdDPKZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhFdDPKZ.jpg&h=9ba2a237&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一係就話人無入機場俾人拉都抵死<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KXzogpZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKXzogpZ.jpg&h=0299a461&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">航膳閪路 #155949</span>又係你呀<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T2shkRF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT2shkRF.jpg&h=2faed15e&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">我唔知佢地係真心講定假膠，但呢種宣傳手法只會令人更加反感<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong>"},{"pid":"e85c8dfec9f7a4f59c4d2c6626d9163bb410d5db","tid":1502342,"uid":286964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T15:50:53.000Z","msg":"借位<br />\n<br />\n(正經)(請給我長期置頂) 整合被控義士進程 一個也不能少不是口號！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1502159\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1502159</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"7bb2dfb9ae30eb871232b90171f6cee7300edb40","tid":1502342,"uid":43994,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T15:51:54.000Z","msg":"825 荃葵青"},{"pid":"86a78494eadfc47e09ec71f456b1489130c54b70","tid":1502342,"uid":43994,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T15:52:45.000Z","msg":"825 荃葵青"},{"pid":"099547c847b3f51037cae135228477e3c7c6390f","tid":1502342,"uid":43994,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T15:53:33.000Z","msg":"825 荃葵青"},{"pid":"703f4f90d8d3490c60bb2d72d8d8b738706cf11f","tid":1502342,"uid":43994,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T15:54:08.000Z","msg":"825 荃葵青"},{"pid":"6076e757ce3fc092d769eef6d7ea57204e2a3f69","tid":1502342,"uid":43994,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T15:56:03.000Z","msg":"825 荃葵青"},{"pid":"1b244ba535a46b690023f58f511dcbb9666f353d","tid":1502342,"uid":47042,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T15:58:23.000Z","msg":"機場係春袋就更加要預早吹大雞<br />\n而唔係最後一刻起連登叫人<br />\n<br />\n仲要明明有其他活動，不反對通知書都攞埋"},{"pid":"c23d91ed5cda8617a2e1197727065c540efb0345","tid":1502342,"uid":94640,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T16:01:30.000Z","msg":"其實818之後唔係話升級去機場?<br />\n要去就要一連幾日，一日既話同打八號波一樣，迫唔到佢地跪"},{"pid":"8cd98d874d68ad291f94ec4b0848b47181e48b78","tid":1502342,"uid":43994,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1b244ba535a46b690023f58f511dcbb9666f353d","tid":1502342,"uid":47042,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T15:58:23.000Z","msg":"機場係春袋就更加要預早吹大雞<br />\n而唔係最後一刻起連登叫人<br />\n<br />\n仲要明明有其他活動，不反對通知書都攞埋"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T16:02:06.000Z","msg":"啱呀<br />\n依家啲遊行都係一兩個星期前開始準備<br />\n機場都用返一兩個星期做宣傳吹雞都唔過份<br />\n次次都臨時臨急仲要撞活動 都仲要吹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"